title: Remarks by President Biden After Air Force One Arrival | The White House
content: Joint Base AndrewsPrince George’s County, Maryland5:27 P.M. ESTQ    Any update on the situation in Ukraine?THE PRESIDENT:  I didn’t hear you.Q    Any update on the situation in Ukraine?THE PRESIDENT:  No, not in the last couple hours.Q    Have you decided how soon you would be moving U.S. troops to Eastern Europe?THE PRESIDENT:  I’ll be moving U.S. troops to Eastern Europe and the NATO countries in the near term — not a lot.5:28 P.M.
